    "text": [
        "Dear Sir or Madam,",
        "I am writing this letter to bring to your notice about a charger I recently ordered from you. I have received a faulty product and I would like to have it replaced.",
        "I ordered a charger for my phone on 12th October from you and the order number is #12345678. I have also paid for the order using my Paypal account. I was excited to receive the order on the same day but once after I opened it, I noticed that the pin on the adapter was broken and because of this I am unable to use the product. I regularly order from your site and never have I faced any issue like this and it is indeed disappointing to see such an established company sending faulty products like",
